data.description: This Stunning five bedroom home located in a cul-de-sac in Bayou Lakes, is the one you have been searching for. This two story home has a private office, formal dining, a grand staircase, High ceilings in the main living room, a beautiful spacious kitchen with a large granite Island. Ample cabinets. A lovely fireplace in the living room. Kitchen is open to the living room. Excellent for entertaining. There are three full bathrooms and one half bath.  13,000 Sqft+ homesite, this is one of the largest lots in Bayou Lakes. The lovely neighborhood pool, splashpad, and park are very near by. Schedule your showing today.
